begin\": 2262, \"end\": 2265, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_E._Lee\", \"score\": 0.9201397032435343, \"rank\": 0.08336851348101275, \"text\": \"Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_E._Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_E._Lee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, the Waterford Gallery of Art SETU Graduate Award Commission will officially launch a newly commissioned portrait of Olympic silver medal winner John Treacy, by recent SETU Waterford Visual Arts Graduate, Sammy Kane.\", \"from\": 2274, \"to\": 2500, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2429, \"end\": 2440, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Treacy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"John Treacy\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Treacy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Treacy\"}, {\"begin\": 2489, \"end\": 2494, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sammy_Corporation\", \"score\": 0.9659666850255102, \"rank\": 0.0351831740781023, \"text\": \"Sammy\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sammy_Corporation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sammy_Corporation\"}, {\"begin\": 2495, \"end\": 2499, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dany_Kane\", \"score\": 0.9999999985686827, \"rank\": 1.3986210173469256e-09, \"text\": \"Kane\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q2159907\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dany_Kane\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dany_Kane\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The exhibition is being staged with support from the Waterford Arts Office, Creative Ireland and the Olympic Federation of Ireland.\", \"from\": 2502, \"to\": 2633, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2555, \"end\": 2564, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Waterford_GAA\", \"score\": 0.9559702864150018, \"rank\": 0.044643517651250485, \"text\": \"Waterford